narrator: *The hero animates falling down a steep hill. The hero is badly hurt*
protagonist: *text buble* What... WHAT IS THAT THING? I got to get away! Away from it! I must go on despite my grave injuries!
narrator: Your health is low, so you better make a run for it! The units movement options is visualized by blue highligts on each tile. Click on the tile furthest away from the monster chasing you.
protagonist: *the monster follows you* Ahh, it keeps following me! I need to hide!
narrator: *you come across some running water* The terrain you move across affects your movement range. Try moving over the running water.